###Block:Animal Companion Size work-around
#
# These bonuses prevent the listed animals from increasing in size when they gain hit dice as a companion
# This should eventually be done by hard-coding it but for now this work-around will let the 5.8 companions come out with the correct numbers - Eddy
# Class of the Master	Type				Adjust PC Size
FOLLOWER:AnimalCompanionLVL1=3	TYPE:Animal Companion	BONUS:SIZEMOD|NUMBER|-1|PRERACE:1,Wolf,Dire Animal (Dire Rat)|PREVARGT:TL,3|PREVARLT:TL,7
FOLLOWER:AnimalCompanionLVL2=3	TYPE:Animal Companion	BONUS:SIZEMOD|NUMBER|-1|PRERACE:1,Wolf,Dire Animal (Dire Rat)|PREVARGT:TL,3|PREVARLT:TL,7
FOLLOWER:AnimalCompanionLVL3=3	TYPE:Animal Companion	BONUS:SIZEMOD|NUMBER|-1|PRERACE:1,Wolf,Dire Animal (Dire Rat)|PREVARGT:TL,3|PREVARLT:TL,7
#

